<h2 id="troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</h2>

<p>Personally I have run into errors when trying to populateÂ <strong><em>variables located in partials</em></strong>Â with YAML values, so the work around is to have all the Sass variables on our main SCSS file and use @import for the actual styles. Also, weÂ <em>cannot</em>Â process Sass partials with Jekyll (meaning we cannot have empty frontmatter (â€”) in the partial files). At least it didnâ€™t work for me, so if you know more, please leave more comments below!</p>
